lead_paragraph: DUEL IN THE STREETS OF BROWNSVILLE.--We learn by a gentleman recently from Brownsville, Texas, that a duel took place in the streets of that town on Sunday last, which terminated fatally to one of the parties. Mr. Clark, an officer in tile custom house, had a difficulty with Mr. Harry Harison, which came near resulting in a duel, but was finally adjusted.
